(606, '4194', '2025-10-07', '2PM-4PM', 'Project Refinement', 'In this session, I started implementing the changes suggested by my senior during the earlier meeting. I carefully reviewed the feedback and began updating my Spring Boot project accordingly.\r\n\r\nKey tasks included:\r\n\r\nAnalyzing the existing CRUD logic to identify areas for optimization.\r\n\r\nModifying service layer methods to improve performance and code readability.\r\n\r\nAdding proper validation checks to ensure data integrity before database operations.\r\n\r\nUpdating exception handling mechanisms for better error reporting.\r\n\r\nOutcome:\r\n\r\nCompleted part of the suggested modifications.\r\n\r\nImproved the overall structure and maintainability of the code.\r\n\r\nPrepared the remaining tasks for the next working session.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
(607, '4194', '2025-10-07', '4PM-6PM', 'Implementation and Testing', 'During this time, I continued with the remaining modifications as per the seniorâs suggestions and performed testing to verify that all CRUD operations were functioning correctly after the updates.\r\n\r\nKey activities:\r\n\r\nCompleted implementation of all feedback-related changes.\r\n\r\nConducted testing for Create, Read, Update, and Delete operations using Postman.\r\n\r\nVerified API responses, status codes, and data consistency in the database.\r\n\r\nDocumented all updates made for future reference.\r\nOutcome:\r\n\r\nAll suggested changes successfully implemented and tested.\r\n\r\nProject performance and reliability improved.\r\n\r\nReady for re-evaluation or deployment review by senior.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
