(837, '4196', '2025-10-15', '9AM-11AM', 'Hitz Crafty Website â Registration Module Development', 'Started development of my own website âHitz Craftyâ using Spring Boot, Thymeleaf, and Bootstrap CSS. Completed the user registration module, integrating both frontend and backend functionality.\r\nSet up the Spring Boot project structure for the âHitz Craftyâ website and configured required dependencies for Spring Web, Spring MVC, Thymeleaf, Spring Data JPA, and Bootstrap CSS.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
