(900, '4196', '2025-10-17', '2PM-4PM', 'Hitz Crafty Website â Home Page and User Dashboard Development', 'Created the User Dashboard section to display logged-in user information (like name, email, etc.) fetched from the database. Integrated backend data with Thymeleaf templates.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(901, '4196', '2025-10-17', '4PM-6PM', 'Hitz Crafty Website â Home Page and User Dashboard Development', 'Enhanced the overall frontend design of the home and dashboard pages using Bootstrap CSS for responsiveness and better UI. Tested the complete login-to-dashboard navigation flow successfully.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(902, '4194', '2025-10-17', '9AM-11AM', 'JavaScript â Array Methods', 'Studied and implemented various Array methods in JavaScript.\r\n\r\nPracticed methods like map(), filter(), reduce(), forEach(), find(), some(), and every().\r\n\r\nUnderstood how these methods help in iterating, transforming, and filtering array elements efficiently.\r\n\r\nImplemented small programs to observe how each method behaves differently.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
(903, '4194', '2025-10-17', '11AM-1PM', 'JavaScript â Functions and Methods', 'Learned the concept of functions (declaration, expression, and arrow functions).\r\n\r\nStudied the difference between functions and methods (functions defined inside an object).\r\n\r\nExplored how to use parameters, return values, and scope in JavaScript functions.\r\n\r\nPracticed writing reusable functions to make code more modular and maintainable.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
(904, '4194', '2025-10-17', '4PM-6PM', 'JavaScript â Window Object', 'Explored the Window object in JavaScript which represents the browser window.\r\n\r\nLearned about properties like window.innerWidth, window.innerHeight, and methods such as alert(), confirm(), and prompt().\r\n\r\nUnderstood how global variables and functions are part of the window object in browsers.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
(905, '4194', '2025-10-17', '2PM-4PM', 'JavaScript â DOM (Document Object Model)', 'Learned about the DOM structure and how JavaScript interacts with HTML elements.\r\n\r\nPracticed selecting and modifying elements using methods like getElementById(), querySelector(), and getElementsByClassName().\r\n\r\nAdded interactivity by dynamically changing content, styles, and attributes.\r\n\r\nImplemented small examples to understand event handling (onclick, addEventListener).', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
(906, '4196', '2025-10-20', '9AM-11AM', 'Hitz Crafty Website â Home Page Enhancement (Navbar, Name, and Logo)', 'Enhanced the Home Page of the Hitz Crafty website by adding a responsive navigation bar, logo, and brand name using Spring Boot, Thymeleaf, and Bootstrap CSS for better UI and user experience.\r\nIn this time Opened the Hitz Crafty home page template and planned the UI structure for adding the navigation bar and brand section.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(907, '4196', '2025-10-20', '11AM-1PM', 'Hitz Crafty Website â Home Page Enhancement (Navbar, Name, and Logo)', 'Implemented the Navbar using Bootstrap CSS for a responsive layout. Added navigation links such as Home, Products.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(908, '4196', '2025-10-20', '2PM-4PM', 'Hitz Crafty Website â Home Page Enhancement (Navbar, Name, and Logo)', 'In this time i Added the website name (\"Hitz Crafty\") and integrated the logo image on the navbar using Thymeleaf template syntax for consistent branding across pages.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(909, '4196', '2025-10-20', '4PM-6PM', 'Hitz Crafty Website â Home Page Enhancement (Navbar, Name, and Logo)', 'Improved the styling and alignment of the navbar and logo for a clean, modern look. Tested the design across multiple pages to ensure proper responsiveness and consistent appearance.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(910, '4196', '2025-10-21', '9AM-11AM', 'Hitz Crafty Website â Home Page Enhancement (Navbar, Name, and Logo)', 'Completed the Home Page Navbar setup with brand name and logo using Spring Boot, Thymeleaf, and Bootstrap CSS for a polished user interface.\r\nIn this time Planned the home page structure and layout for the navigation bar and brand section.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(911, '4196', '2025-10-21', '11AM-1PM', 'Hitz Crafty Website â Home Page Enhancement (Navbar, Name, and Logo)', 'setup with brand name and logo using Spring Boot, Thymeleaf, and Bootstrap CSS for a polished user interface.\r\nIn this time Created a responsive Navbar using Bootstrap CSS and added navigation links (Home, Products, About, Contact).', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(912, '4196', '2025-10-21', '2PM-4PM', 'Hitz Crafty Website â Home Page Enhancement (Navbar, Name, and Logo)', 'Integrated the logo image and brand name (\"Hitz Crafty\") using Thymeleaf to make it dynamic and consistent across all pages.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(913, '3697', '2025-10-21', '9AM-11AM', 'Learning & Practice', 'Revised core Java concepts including loops, conditionals, and string handling.\r\nâ¢ Practiced JDBC connectivity by writing programs for database interaction using Statement and PreparedStatement.\r\nâ¢ Explored basic CRUD operations in Java with MySQL integration.\r\nâ¢ Reviewed Spring Boot fundamentals including project structure, annotations, and dependency management.\r\nâ¢ Worked on improving communication skills and resume presentation.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yandra Ravi Babu'),
