(939, '4196', '2025-10-22', '4PM-6PM', 'Home Page â Navbar & Logo (Hitz Crafty Website)', 'Applied final CSS styling and responsiveness to the Navbar and Logo for a professional look across all devices.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(940, '4196', '2025-10-23', '9AM-11AM', 'Product Cards & Images Section (Hitz Crafty Website)', 'During this time, I will focus on designing the overall structure and layout for the product cards section on the home page. Iâll plan how each product should appear â including its image, name, price, and a short description â while ensuring the layout is clean and visually appealing. Iâll also decide on the column arrangement using Bootstrapâs grid system to maintain responsiveness across desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(941, '4196', '2025-10-23', '11AM-1PM', 'Product Cards & Images Section (Hitz Crafty Website)', 'In this session, I will start implementing the product cards on the home page using Bootstrap components. Each product card will include a product image, product title, and pricing details. Iâll use sample or dummy data initially to visualize the structure. During this time, Iâll also ensure that the design remains uniform, properly spaced, and aligned for a neat presentation.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(942, '4196', '2025-10-23', '2PM-4PM', 'Product Cards & Images Section (Hitz Crafty Website)', 'In the afternoon, I will work on integrating dynamic data into the product cards using Thymeleaf templates. This step will connect the frontend with the backend so that products stored in the database can be displayed automatically on the web page. Iâll also test the data flow from the controller to the view to make sure the integration works smoothly.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
