(969, '4196', '2025-10-24', '4PM-6PM', 'Tic Tac Toe Game Development (Using HTML, CSS, JavaScript)', 'I added game reset functionality and result display. When a player wins or the match ends in a draw, a message is shown, and the board can be reset for a new round. I also tested the full flow of the game to ensure smooth working of both frontend visuals and game logic. Minor styling improvements and responsive adjustments were made to ensure the game runs properly on different screen sizes.\r\nToday, I successfully developed a fully functional Tic Tac Toe Game using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The project includes an interactive 3x3 grid, player turn switching, win/draw detection, and a reset option â all designed with responsive and user-friendly styling.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
