(988, '4196', '2025-10-27', '9AM-11AM', 'Weather Dashboard Creation', 'During this session, I began by designing the basic layout and structure of the Weather Dashboard using HTML. I created input fields for entering the city name, a search button, and sections to display weather details such as temperature, humidity, and wind speed. I also planned the UI layout and how different weather data components would appear on the screen.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
