(993, '4196', '2025-10-27', '11AM-1PM', 'Weather Dashboard Creation', 'In this time block, I worked on styling the dashboard using CSS. I added color schemes, background gradients, and card designs for weather data display. I also focused on making the layout responsive so that it adjusts properly across various devices like laptops, tablets, and phones. and I implemented the JavaScript functionality to connect the dashboard with the OpenWeather API. I wrote code to fetch live weather data based on the city name entered by the user. I tested multiple city inputs and handled cases where the city was not found by displaying an error message.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(994, '4196', '2025-10-27', '2PM-4PM', 'Weather Dashboard Creation', 'I focused on enhancing interactivity and data presentation. I formatted the fetched weather data (temperature, humidity, wind speed, and conditions) and displayed it neatly on the dashboard. I also added icons and background changes according to the weather type (like sunny, rainy, or cloudy). Finally, I reviewed and debugged the code to ensure everything worked smoothly.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(995, '4196', '2025-10-27', '4PM-6PM', 'Weather Dashboard Creation', ' I tested multiple city inputs and handled cases where the city was not found by displaying an error message.\r\nToday, I developed a fully functional Weather Dashboard Application using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The app fetches real-time weather data from the OpenWeather API and displays it in a visually appealing dashboard with responsive design and error handling features.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(996, '4194', '2025-10-27', '9AM-11AM', 'Styling & Animations', 'Polished CSS: buttons styling, hover/active states, and a simple transition when result appears. Added small animations for choice reveal (scale + fade) and result flash. Improved accessibility: added aria-labels to buttons and semantic roles for result area.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
(997, '4194', '2025-10-27', '11AM-1PM', 'Styling & Animations', 'Polished CSS: buttons styling, hover/active states, and a simple transition when result appears. Added small animations for choice reveal (scale + fade) and result flash. Improved accessibility: added aria-labels to buttons and semantic roles for result area.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
(998, '4194', '2025-10-27', '2PM-4PM', 'Features & Testing', 'Implemented scoreboard (wins / losses / draws) and reset button. Added persistent score using localStorage so scores survive refresh. Manual testing across Chrome and Firefox; fixed logic edge-cases (ties and rapid clicks). Wrote inline comments in JS for readability.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
(999, '4194', '2025-10-27', '4PM-6PM', 'Final polish & Deployment preperation', 'Fixed visual bugs (button alignment on small screens), optimized CSS for fewer repaint triggers. Created README with game description, features, and instructions to run locally. Prepared files for deployment and tested index.html locally. Next steps: push to GitHub Pages or Netlify and add unit tests for game logic.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
