(1039, '4196', '2025-10-30', '4PM-6PM', 'Light On/Off application using (HTML, CSS, JavaScript, and Bootstrap)', 'I enhanced the user interface and functionality. I centered the content, adjusted button spacing, and applied hover effects for better interactivity. I also tested the project in different browsers to ensure compatibility. Finally, I reviewed the full flow â clicking âTurn Onâ displays the glowing bulb, and âTurn Offâ returns it to the dim image.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
