(1074, '4196', '2025-11-03', '4PM-6PM', 'Hitz Crafty Project â Email Verification Setup Using Brevo', 'I tested the entire email verification flow end-to-end. I registered multiple test users to ensure each received a verification email from Brevo. After clicking the verification link, their status updated successfully in the database. I also refined the email template, adding the âWelcome to Hitz Craftyâ message along with verification instructions for a professional look.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1075, '4194', '2025-11-03', '9AM-11AM', 'Project Presentation Preparation', 'Prepared for a meeting with the senior regarding ongoing projects. Reviewed the Tic-Tac-Toe game project, ensuring all features in HTML, CSS, and JavaScript were working correctly. Organized notes to explain the project logic, UI design, and code implementation clearly.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
(1076, '4194', '2025-11-03', '11AM-1PM', 'Project Review â Tic-Tac-Toe Game', 'Attended a review meeting with the senior to present the Tic-Tac-Toe Game Project.\r\n\r\nDemonstrated all key features including UI design, player turn logic, win/draw detection, and reset functionality.\r\n\r\nReceived constructive feedback and implemented the suggested improvements during the session itself.\r\n\r\nEnhanced the projectâs functionality and user experience as per feedback.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
(1077, '4194', '2025-11-03', '2PM-4PM', 'Project Presentation â Staff Management System', 'Presented the Staff Management System project.\r\n\r\nFrontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript\r\nBackend: Spring Boot\r\n\r\nExplained CRUD operations (Create, Read, Update, Delete) and described how the frontend interacts with the backend.\r\n\r\nDetailed the project architecture and communication flow between modules.\r\n\r\nReceived positive feedback and appreciation from the senior for both UI design and project implementation.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
