(1093, '4196', '2025-11-04', '4PM-6PM', 'Hitz Crafty Project â Add to Cart Functionality Implementation', 'I tested and refined the complete Add to Cart flow. I verified that multiple products can be added, quantities can be updated, and items can be removed correctly. I improved the UI to display cart items neatly and ensured that cart data persists correctly in the database. Minor UI adjustments and validations were added for a smoother user experience.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1094, '4194', '2025-11-04', '9AM-11AM', 'UI & Core Game Logic', 'Created the initial HTML structure for the Rock-Paper-Scissors game, including buttons for Rock, Paper, and Scissors, a result display area, and a score section. Implemented the core game logic in JavaScript to handle user choice, generate random computer choice, and determine the result (win/lose/draw). Added basic CSS for layout and made the container responsive for both mobile and desktop screens.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
(1095, '4194', '2025-11-04', '11AM-1PM', 'Styling & Animations', 'Enhanced CSS by improving button styling, adding hover and active effects, and implementing smooth transitions when results appear. Introduced subtle animations for choice reveals (scale and fade effects) and result highlighting. Improved accessibility with aria-labels and semantic roles for key interactive elements.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
(1096, '4194', '2025-11-04', '2PM-4PM', 'Features & Testing', 'Added a scoreboard to track wins, losses, and draws, along with a reset button. Integrated localStorage to persist scores after page refresh. Performed manual testing across Chrome and Firefox, resolving logic edge cases like ties and rapid clicks. Included inline comments in JavaScript to improve readability and code clarity.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
(1097, '4194', '2025-11-04', '4PM-6PM', 'Final Polish & Deployment Preparation', 'Fixed minor UI bugs such as button alignment issues on small screens. Optimized CSS to reduce unnecessary reflows and repaints. Created a detailed README file containing the project description, key features, and local setup instructions. Verified functionality through local testing and prepared files for deployment on GitHub Pages or Netlify. Next steps include adding unit tests for game logic.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
