(1100, '4196', '2025-11-05', '9AM-11AM', 'Rock Paper Scissors Game Development  ? 9:00 AM â 11:00 AM:', 'I started by planning the Rock Paper Scissors game structure and finalizing the layout design. I created the base HTML file with three main options â Rock, Paper, and Scissors â along with a display area for showing the results. The UI was structured using Bootstrap to make it responsive and visually appealing.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1101, '4196', '2025-11-05', '11AM-1PM', 'Rock Paper Scissors Game Development', 'Next, I worked on styling the game using CSS and Bootstrap classes. I designed attractive buttons for the three choices, added hover effects, and styled the score and message section to give a modern game-like look. I also ensured the layout adapts properly on both desktop and mobile screens.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
