(1134, '4194', '2025-11-07', '11AM-1PM', 'Project Setup & Create API Implementation', 'Created: VenueEntity (Entity class with fields like id, name, location, capacity, etc.) VenueRepository (extends JpaRepository) Implemented Create (POST) API to insert new venue records into the database Tested API successfully in Postman', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
(1135, '4194', '2025-11-07', '2PM-4PM', 'Spring Boot CRUD Operations â Read API', 'Implemented Read (GET) APIs: GET /venues ? Fetch all venue records GET /venues/{id} ? Fetch specific record by ID Added Service layer for better architecture: Controller ? Service ? Repository pattern Implemented custom exception handling for âRecord Not Foundâ Verified all endpoints using Postman', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
