(1140, '3697', '2025-11-10', '9AM-11AM', 'Learning', 'Continued learning the concepts of Spring Boot â focused on entity relationships and integrating Thymeleaf with controllers.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yandra Ravi Babu'),
(1141, '3697', '2025-11-10', '11AM-1PM', 'Learning & Practice', 'Continued learning the concepts of Spring Boot â focused on entity relationships and integrating Thymeleaf with controllers.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yandra Ravi Babu'),
(1142, '3697', '2025-11-10', '2PM-4PM', 'Learning & Practice', 'Continued learning the concepts of Spring Boot â focused on entity relationships and integrating Thymeleaf with controllers.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yandra Ravi Babu'),
(1143, '4196', '2025-11-10', '9AM-11AM', 'React â Forms and Event Handling', 'Iâll begin by revising React props and state from the previous day to ensure clarity before moving on to new concepts. Then, Iâll start learning about event handling in React, including how to handle user actions such as button clicks, input changes, and form submissions using event handlers like onClick, onChange, and onSubmit.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1144, '4196', '2025-11-10', '11AM-1PM', 'React â Forms and Event Handling', 'In this session, Iâll practice creating controlled components â input fields where the value is managed by React state. Iâll build simple examples like a login form and feedback form, where the data entered by the user is stored in the componentâs state using useState() and updated dynamically.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1145, '4073', '2025-11-10', '4PM-6PM', 'A single-threaded object that provides methods for interacting with the database', 'A single-threaded object that provides methods for interacting with the database', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'SHANMUKH ASAI SASTRY KALAJULAPATI '),
(1146, '4196', '2025-11-10', '2PM-4PM', 'React â Forms and Event Handling', 'Next, Iâll learn how to manage multiple form fields and validation. Iâll explore how to prevent default form submissions using event.preventDefault() and display validation messages dynamically. Iâll also work on improving user experience with proper input types and labels.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1147, '4196', '2025-11-10', '4PM-6PM', 'React â Forms and Event Handling', 'Iâll create a complete React registration form project that includes name, email, and password fields with validation and submit handling. Iâll apply Bootstrap for styling, ensuring a clean, responsive layout. At the end, Iâll test the app and log all entered data in the console to verify successful event handling.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1148, '4194', '2025-11-10', '9AM-11AM', 'Spring Boot CRUD Operations â Read API', 'Implemented Read (GET) APIs: GET /venues ? Fetch all venue records GET /venues/{id} ? Fetch specific record by ID Added Service layer for better architecture: Controller ? Service ? Repository pattern Implemented custom exception handling for âRecord Not Foundâ Verified all endpoints using Postman', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
