(1152, '4196', '2025-11-11', '9AM-11AM', 'To-Do List Application Development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)', 'I started the day by planning the structure of the To-Do List app. I designed the layout using HTML, which included an input field for entering tasks, an âAdd Taskâ button, and a section to display the task list. I ensured a clean and semantic structure with proper use of div, input, and ul/li elements.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1153, '4196', '2025-11-11', '11AM-1PM', 'To-Do List Application Development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)', 'Next, I worked on styling the application using CSS. I focused on creating a modern and minimal UI â centered layout, shadow effects for the task box, hover animations for buttons, and a responsive design that adjusts well on both desktop and mobile. I also applied color themes to make the interface look professional and engaging', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1154, '3697', '2025-11-11', '9AM-11AM', 'Learning the concepts of Spring Boot', 'Studied Spring Boot framework structure, project setup, and main components (starter dependencies, annotations, and auto-configuration).', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yandra Ravi Babu'),
(1155, '3697', '2025-11-11', '11AM-1PM', 'Practical Implementation', 'Implemented a simple Spring Boot project with Student entity, repository, service, and controller layers using Thymeleaf templates for frontend integration.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yandra Ravi Babu'),
(1156, '3697', '2025-11-11', '2PM-4PM', 'Debugging and Testing', 'Fixed getter method issues in the Student class, tested CRUD operations, and verified data flow between controller and view.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yandra Ravi Babu'),
(1157, '4196', '2025-11-11', '2PM-4PM', 'To-Do List Application Development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)', 'In this session, I implemented the JavaScript logic for the To-Do app. I wrote functions to add new tasks dynamically, display them in the list, and mark tasks as completed. I also learned to use DOM manipulation methods like createElement(), appendChild(), and removeChild() to handle list updates.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1158, '4073', '2025-11-11', '9AM-11AM', ' Do I need to import java.lang package any time', ' Do I need to import java.lang package any time', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'SHANMUKH ASAI SASTRY KALAJULAPATI '),
