(1196, '4194', '2025-11-13', '2PM-4PM', 'CRUD Operations Implementation', 'Developed and tested CRUD operations for teacher details â including APIs for Add, View, Update, and Delete teachers using RESTful endpoints. Verified functionality using Postman.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
