(1198, '4196', '2025-11-14', '9AM-11AM', 'Calendar Application Development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)', 'I started by creating the basic layout of the calendar using HTML.\r\nAdded a header section to display current month and year.\r\nAdded previous and next buttons for month navigation.\r\nCreated a grid structure using table / div for days of the week and date boxes.\r\nEnsured clean and semantic HTML for easy styling and script integration.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1199, '4196', '2025-11-14', '11AM-1PM', 'Calendar Application Development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)', 'Next, I focused on designing a clean and modern calendar UI using CSS.\r\nUsed Flexbox/Grid to align date boxes properly.\r\nStyled the month header, navigation buttons, and day labels.\r\nAdded hover effects, shadows, and color themes.\r\nEnsured the layout is responsive for mobile and desktop screens.\r\nHighlighted the current date with a special background color.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1200, '4196', '2025-11-14', '2PM-4PM', 'Calendar Application Development (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)w', 'During this time, I added full JavaScript functionality to the calendar.\r\nDisplayed current month dates dynamically using JS Date() object.\r\nWrote functions for previous month and next month navigation.\r\nAutomatically adjusted days according to month length and leap years.\r\nEnsured correct alignment of days starting from the right weekday.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
