(1210, '4196', '2025-11-17', '9AM-11AM', 'Portfolio Website Development (React.js)', 'I started by setting up the React environment.\r\nCreated a new React project using Vite / Create React App.\r\nCleaned unnecessary default files.\r\nSet up a proper folder structure:\r\ncomponents/\r\npages/\r\nassets/\r\nstyles/\r\nInstalled required packages like React Router, Bootstrap / Tailwind, etc.\r\nPrepared the basic layout of the portfolio.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
