(1270, '4194', '2025-11-21', '9AM-11AM', 'Project Meeting â J2C Project', 'Attended a meeting with the senior and teammates regarding the J2C project. Each team member described their respective tasks. Senior assigned new tasks to everyone based on project requirements.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Muskan'),
