(1274, '4196', '2025-11-24', '9AM-11AM', 'J2C Website âJob Description section ', 'Job Description Model & Bean Creation\r\nStarted by creating the Model/Bean class for Job Description.\r\nAdded important fields like:\r\njobId\r\njobTitle\r\njobLocation\r\njobType\r\njobSummary\r\nskillsRequired\r\nsalaryRange\r\njobResponsibilities\r\nAdded getters, setters, and constructors.\r\nEnsured proper encapsulation for secure data handling.\r\nand meeting with Anita discuss about the this project ', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1275, '4196', '2025-11-24', '11AM-1PM', 'J2C Website âJob Description section', 'AO Layer (Database Connectivity)\r\nCreated the DAO class for Job Description.\r\nAdded database logic for:\r\nInserting job description\r\nFetching the job description\r\nUpdating job description\r\nDeleting job description\r\nConnected MySQL/PostgreSQL DB using JDBC.\r\nTested the DB connectivity and SQL queries.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1276, '3697', '2025-11-24', '9AM-11AM', 'Learning & Practice', 'Learned and practiced Spring Boot concepts.\r\n\r\nWorked on Thymeleaf templates and explored proper usage of getters in the Student entity.\r\n\r\nDebugged issues related to image paths in HTML and corrected the <img> tag usage.\r\n\r\nReviewed and updated JDBC & MySQL configuration understanding.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yandra Ravi Babu'),
