(1407, '4196', '2025-12-09', '9AM-11AM', 'Convert J2C Project to use Lambda & Stream API', 'Identified all places where normal loops are used\r\n(DAO, Servlet, JSP data handling, utility classes)\r\nListed which sections can be converted into:\r\nStream filtering\r\nSorting\r\nMapping\r\nCollecting\r\nOptional usage\r\nUpdated model classes if needed for cleaner stream operations\r\nChecked Java version supports Stream API (Java 8+)', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1408, '4196', '2025-12-09', '11AM-1PM', 'Convert J2C Project to use Lambda & Stream API', 'Converted ResultSet list data into streams\r\nReplaced manual for loops with:\r\n.stream()\r\n.map()\r\n.filter()\r\n.collect(Collectors.toList())\r\nExample changes:\r\nFiltering organizations by city\r\nSorting by employees count\r\nMapping database rows to model using lambda\r\nCleaned old code & replaced with compact lambda expressions\r\nOutcome: DAO is fully upgraded with Lambda + Stream API.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1409, '4196', '2025-12-09', '2PM-4PM', 'Convert J2C Project to use Lambda & Stream API', 'Replaced loops in Servlets with Stream operations\r\nConverted code for:\r\nValidations using Optional\r\nSearching records using .filter()\r\nRemoving unwanted data using .removeIf()\r\nGrouping values if required using .collect(Collectors.groupingBy())\r\nImproved readability of data flow from DAO ? Service ? Servlet', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1410, '4196', '2025-12-09', '4PM-6PM', 'Convert J2C Project to use Lambda & Stream API', 'Tested all pages:\r\nJob Details\r\nCandidate Preferences\r\n Job Description\r\n Communication\r\n Organization Details\r\nEnsured Stream API outputs same or better results\r\nOptimized:\r\nNo duplicate records\r\nData loads fast\r\nClean code (no warnings)\r\nAdded comments for understanding stream operations', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1411, '4196', '2025-12-10', '9AM-11AM', 'Add Pagination, Sorting & Filtering to J2C Project', 'Decide page size (e.g., 5 or 10 records per page)\r\nImplement pagination using Stream API:\r\n.skip((page-1) * pageSize)\r\n.limit(pageSize)\r\nModify DAO or Service layer to support:\r\ncurrentPage\r\ntotalPages\r\nrecordsCount\r\nAdd PaginationDTO (optional) to carry data.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1412, '4196', '2025-12-10', '11AM-1PM', 'Add Pagination, Sorting & Filtering to J2C Project', 'Add sorting options:\r\nSort by Name\r\nSort by City\r\nSort by Employees\r\nSort by Industry\r\nImplement Stream sorting:\r\n.sorted(Comparator.comparing(Organization::getName))\r\nAdd dropdown on JSP:\r\nSort By: Name | City | Employees | Industry\r\nApply selected sort to the list before pagination.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
