(1417, '4196', '2025-12-10', '2PM-4PM', 'Add Pagination, Sorting & Filtering to J2C Project', 'Add search filters:\r\nSearch by Company Name\r\nFilter by City\r\nFilter by Industry\r\nStream filters example:\r\n.filter(o -> o.getCity().equalsIgnoreCase(cityFilter))\r\n.filter(o -> o.getName().contains(searchKeyword))\r\nAdd search bar in JSP\r\nAdd dropdown:\r\nCity: Delhi, Mumbai, Bangaloreâ¦\r\nIndustry: IT, Finance, Retailâ¦', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1418, '4196', '2025-12-10', '4PM-6PM', 'Add Pagination, Sorting & Filtering to J2C Project', 'Combine all three features smoothly:\r\nFirst Filter\r\nThen Sort\r\nFinally Paginate\r\nTest various combinations:\r\nFilter + Sort\r\nPagination + Sort\r\nFilter + Pagination\r\nFix UI navigation issues (Next, Previous buttons)\r\nAdd Bootstrap styles for clean UI.', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
