(1455, '4196', '2025-12-18', '9AM-11AM', 'Authentication flow, Protected Routes).', 'Understood authentication flow in React\r\n(Login ? Token ? Access Protected Pages)\r\nDesigned basic auth structure:\r\nLogin page\r\nLogout functionality\r\nAuth context\r\nCreated AuthContext using Context API\r\nStored auth state (isAuthenticated, user)\r\nPlanned token storage strategy (localStorage)', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
