(1463, '4196', '2025-12-19', '9AM-11AM', 'Redux Toolkit & API Integration with Backend', 'Understood why Redux Toolkit is used\r\n\r\nInstalled required packages:\r\n\r\n@reduxjs/toolkit\r\n\r\nreact-redux\r\n\r\nCreated:\r\n\r\nstore.js\r\n\r\nFirst slice using createSlice()\r\n\r\nLearned core concepts:\r\n\r\nStore\r\n\r\nSlice\r\n\r\nReducers\r\n\r\nActions\r\n\r\nConnected Redux store to React app using <Provider>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
(1464, '4196', '2025-12-19', '11AM-1PM', 'Redux Toolkit & API Integration with Backend', 'Created reducers for:\r\n\r\nUser data\r\n\r\nAuthentication state\r\n\r\nProduct list (example)\r\n\r\nUsed:\r\n\r\nuseSelector() to read state\r\n\r\nuseDispatch() to update state\r\n\r\nRemoved prop drilling using Redux global state\r\n\r\nTested state changes via UI buttons/forms', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Jayshree'),
