(1647, '4285', '2026-04-03', '11AM-1PM', 'validation in careerGapRegistration.jsp ', '1)Implemented phone number validation:\r\nIf the user enters less than 10 digits, an error message is displayed in red â âPlease enter a valid 10 digit phone number.â\r\n2)Updated Gap Duration (in years) field:\r\nConverted it into a dropdown with options up to a maximum of 10 years.\r\n3)Developed Primary Skills (Multi-select) feature:\r\nData is fetched dynamically from the master table\r\nUsers can select a maximum of 10 skills only\r\n4)Configured Total Experience (in years) field:\r\nAdded options up to a maximum of 25 years\r\n5)Integrated Last Designation field:\r\nValues are fetched  from the database master table\r\n6)Added Declaration checkbox validation\r\n7)Users must fill all mandatory fields\r\n8)Users must check the declaration checkbox\r\n9)Form submission is restricted if any required field is incomplete or checkbox is not selected', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Vinayaka Siddappa Hachappanavar'),
